_:Ncf601277eafd4010939b3a11338f8b5c <http://schema.org/description> "Border Force is a law enforcement command within the Home Office. We secure the UK border by carrying out immigration and customs controls for people and goods entering the UK. Border Force is part of the Home Office ." .
